---
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-950 via-slate-900 to-blue-900">

  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,#2563eb33,transparent_40%)]"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24">

    <div class="grid items-center gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2">

      <!-- LEFT -->

      <div>

        <span
          class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-blue-600/20 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-300"
        >
          🇸🇬 Built for SMEs & Enterprises
        </span>

        <h1 class="mt-8 text-5xl font-black leading-tight text-white lg:text-6xl">

          Free

          <span class="text-blue-400">

            Free AI Transformation & ROI Assessment

          </span>

        </h1>

        <p class="mt-8 text-xl leading-9 text-slate-300">

          Discover where AI can deliver the greatest business value for your organisation.

In just 3 minutes, receive a personalised AI Transformation Report highlighting priority initiatives, productivity improvements, cost optimisation opportunities and a practical implementation roadmap tailored for your business.

        </p>

        <!-- CTA -->

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">

          <a
            href="#assessment-wizard"
            class="rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-blue-700"
          >

            Start My Free Assessment

          </a>

        </div>

        <!-- Benefits -->

        <div class="mt-12 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 p-5">

            <div class="text-3xl">

              ⏱️

            </div>

            <div class="mt-3 font-bold text-white">

              Takes only 3 minutes

            </div>

          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 p-5">

            <div class="text-3xl">

              💰

            </div>

            <div class="mt-3 font-bold text-white">

              Estimate business impact

            </div>

          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 p-5">

            <div class="text-3xl">

              📈

            </div>

            <div class="mt-3 font-bold text-white">

              Identify transformation opportunities

            </div>

          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 p-5">

            <div class="text-3xl">

              🗺️

            </div>

            <div class="mt-3 font-bold text-white">

              Personalised AI roadmap

            </div>

          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT -->

      <div>

        <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-2xl">

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900">

            Your Personalised Report Includes

          </h2>

          <div class="mt-8 space-y-5">

            <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-5">

              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">

                💰 Business Impact & ROI

              </h3>

              <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">

                Understand where AI can reduce costs and increase profitability.

              </p>

            </div>

            <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-5">

              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">

                ⚡ Productivity Improvements

              </h3>

              <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">

                Identify repetitive work that AI can automate.

              </p>

            </div>

            <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-5">

              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">

                🤖 AI Transformation Recommendations

              </h3>

              <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">

                Discover AI solutions that match your business goals.

              </p>

            </div>

            <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-5">

              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">

                🚀 Transformation Roadmap

              </h3>

              <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">

                Receive an implementation roadmap for your business.

              </p>

            </div>

          </div>

          <!-- Social Proof -->

          <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl bg-blue-50 p-6">

            <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-700">

              Why SME Owners Use This Calculator

            </div>

            <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-700">

              Many businesses know AI is important but aren't sure where to
              begin. This calculator highlights the quickest opportunities
              to save time, reduce costs and improve productivity—without
              requiring any technical knowledge.

            </p>

          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>